&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1-3 years of sales experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong relationship building skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive and target-driven mindset&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear and confident communicator&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to close new business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commitment to an in-office culture — you show up, engage, and grow alongside your team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What’s in It for You?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;First year OTE: $60,000-$75,000 (uncapped)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performance-Based advancement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full benefits + 401(k) match&lt;/li&gt;
