&lt;li&gt;Complete stitch repairs or minor embroidery corrections when necessary.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fold, package, and prepare completed orders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a clean, organized, and safe work environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with other production tasks as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
